title: LF Gold 4ish Jungler for duo to climb with
body:
What the title says, looking for a jungler to duo with to climb into plat with. 

Must be able to stay calm when I tilt and try to keep me focused.
Also Skype would be highly preferred!

Add me in game for a chat and we'll talk to see if we mesh together!

IGN: Staldy

{{sticker:slayer-pantheon-thumbs}}

replies.body: Hey guys, no longer looking for a duo partner, but feel free to add me in game anyway :)
